---
title: Webhook Persistido y Asignación Idempotente
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant API as API pública
    participant Inbox as Billing Webhook Inbox
    participant Worker
    participant App as api:app Orchestrator
    participant Billing as Billing Core
    participant Physical as Physical Core
    participant MP as Mercado Pago

    MP->>API: POST /api/v1/billing/payments/mercadopago/webhook
    API->>API: Validar firma
    API->>Inbox: INSERT provider + providerEventId (unique)
    Inbox-->>API: Persistido o duplicado ya persistido
    API-->>MP: 200 ACK solo después del inbox

    Worker->>Inbox: Tomar evento RECEIVED/FAILED para reintento
    Worker->>MP: Consultar Payment autoritativo
    MP-->>Worker: Movimiento acreditado
    Worker->>App: ConfirmExternalPayment(paymentId, purchaseId)
    App->>Billing: Verificar amount contra quote snapshot
    App->>Physical: confirmCapacity(paymentId, quoteId)
    alt Capacidad completa
        Physical-->>App: CapacityAssignment[]
        App->>Billing: Payment COMPLETED
        App->>Billing: Purchase CAPACITY_ASSIGNED
        App-->>Worker: Procesado
        Worker->>Inbox: status PROCESSED
    else Capacidad fallida con dinero movido
        Physical-->>App: CAPACITY_UNAVAILABLE
        App->>Billing: Payment REQUIRES_MANUAL_REVIEW
        App->>Billing: Purchase EXCEPTION
        App-->>Worker: Excepción persistida
        Worker->>Inbox: status PROCESSED
    else Falla transitoria
        App-->>Worker: RetryableFailure
        Worker->>Inbox: attempts++, nextAttemptAt, status FAILED
    end

